text: Born American (Finnish: J채채t채v채 polte; also known as Arctic Heat) is a 1986 Finnish American action movie directed by first time director Renny Harlin and starring Mike Norris, David Coburn, Piita Vuosalmi, Vesa Vierikko, Thalmus Rasulala, Albert Salmi. ==Other websites== * * Category:1986 action movies Category:Finnish movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies directed by Renny Harlin
